fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Reports section gives you a deeper look at your salon&#x27;s performance beyond the day-to-day. All reports are filterable, exportable, and organised by category so you can find what you need quickly.</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Reports</strong> in the left menu to get started.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Reports are only accessible to admin users.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"finding-a-report\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#finding-a-report\" class=\"peer\">Finding a report</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>The main reports page shows all available reports as cards. You can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search</strong> by report name or description</li>\n<li><strong>Filter by creator</strong> using the All creators dropdown</li>\n<li><strong>Filter by type</strong> using the All reports dropdown</li>\n<li><strong>Browse by category</strong> using the tabs across the top: All reports · Sales · Finance · Appointments · Team · Clients · Inventory</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The left sidebar organises reports into:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>What&#x27;s in it</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>All reports</td><td>Every report in one place</td></tr><tr><td>Favourites</td><td>Reports you&#x27;ve starred for quick access</td></tr><tr><td>Dashboards</td><td>Visual overview reports (e.g. Performance dashboard)</td></tr><tr><td>Premium</td><td>Premium-tier reports</td></tr><tr><td>Folders</td><td>Custom folders you create to organise reports</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Star any report card to add it to your <strong>Favourites</strong>.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"available-reports\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#available-reports\" class=\"peer\">Available reports</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"performance-dashboard\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#performance-dashboard\" class=\"peer\">Performance Dashboard</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p><em>(Dashboards)</em></p>\n<p>A visual overview of your salon&#x27;s performance. Shows key metrics, charts, and trends across revenue, appointments, services, and staff — all in one place.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"sales-log\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#sales-log\" class=\"peer\">Sales Log</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p><em>(Sales)</em></p>\n<p>A detailed record of every sale — including the services sold, discounts applied, payment methods used, staff member, and client. Use this when you need to trace a specific transaction or review sales over a period.</p>\n<p><strong>Filters:</strong> Date range, location, team member, client, payment method.</p>\n<p><strong>Export:</strong> CSV, Excel, PDF.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"finance-summary\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#finance-summary\" class=\"peer\">Finance Summary</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p><em>(Finance)</em></p>\n<p>A period-by-period breakdown of your sales, payments, and liabilities. Perfect for month-end reviews and accounting.</p>\n<p>Choose how to group the data:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>What you&#x27;ll see</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Day</td><td>Last 30 days, one column per day</td></tr><tr><td>Week</td><td>Last 4 weeks</td></tr><tr><td>Month</td><td>Last 6 months (default)</td></tr><tr><td>Quarter</td><td>Last 4 quarters</td></tr><tr><td>Year</td><td>Last 3 years</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p><strong>Export:</strong> CSV, Excel, PDF.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"payment-transactions\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#payment-transactions\" class=\"peer\">Payment Transactions</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p><em>(Finance)</em></p>\n<p>A full log of every individual payment collected. Use this to verify payment method totals or trace a specific transaction.</p>\n<p><strong>Filters:</strong> Date range, location, team member, payment method, transaction type, amount range.</p>\n<p><strong>Export:</strong> CSV, Excel, PDF.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"tips-summary\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#tips-summary\" class=\"peer\">Tips Summary</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p><em>(Team)</em></p>\n<p>An overview of all tips received, broken down by staff member. Shows total tips, number of tipped transactions, average tip, and tip percentage for each person.</p>\n<p><strong>Filters:</strong> Date range, location, team member, payment method.</p>\n<p><strong>Export:</strong> CSV, Excel, PDF.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"export-options\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#export-options\" class=\"peer\">Export options</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>All reports can be exported in:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Format</th><th>Best for</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>CSV</td><td>Importing into a spreadsheet</td></tr><tr><td>Excel (.xlsx)</td><td>A formatted, ready-to-share spreadsheet</td></tr><tr><td>PDF</td><td>Printing or sharing outside the system</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"date-range-options\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#date-range-options\" class=\"peer\">Date range options</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>All reports use the same date picker with quick presets:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Today / Yesterday</li>\n<li>Last 7, 30, or 90 days</li>\n<li>Last week / Last month / Last 3, 6, or 12 months</li>\n<li>Week-to-date / Month-to-date / Quarter-to-date / Year-to-date</li>\n<li>Custom start and end date</li>\n</ul></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs/commission\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Commission</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Set up commission rules for your staff and generate detailed salary slips</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/settings\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Settings</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Configure your branches, business hours, payment methods, and permissions</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-text-align-start size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 5H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M17 19H3\"></path></svg>On this page</h3><div class=\"relative min-h-0 text-sm ms-px overflow-auto [scrollbar-width:none] mask-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,white_16px,white_calc(100%-16px),transparent)] py-3\"><div class=\"relative\"><div data-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-y-0 inset-s-0 bg-fd-primary w-px transition-[clip-path]\" style=\"clip-path:polygon(0 var(--fd-top), 100% var(--fd-top), 100% calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)), 0 calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)))\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col border-s border-fd-foreground/10\"><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#finding-a-report\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Finding a report</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#available-reports\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Available reports</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#performance-dashboard\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0